 A0a_Overview {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "Overview"
  m_sTextData "Delta Force rescues two US diplomats that are being held hostage by foreign anti-US extremists."\
  ""\
  "The following roles MUST be slotted:"\
  "- US Diplomat 1, US Diplomat 2 (hostages)"\
  "- Hostage guards"\
  "- US negotiator, appropriate number of US pilots (number of slotted teams + at least 1)"\
  ""\
  "Only slot hostage or guard if you're capable of engaging in a little roleplay."\
  "Only slot negotiator if you're interested in active & creative negotiation."\
  ""\
  "Note that this mission is NOT strictly about just killing all enemies."\
  "Commanders, hostage guards, negotiator and hostages must read the briefing, you can have an extra 2 minutes for that if you need them."
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
 }
 A0b_Background {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "Background"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Background</h2>"\
  "One week ago, a small anti-western paramilitary cell took two US diplomats hostage to protest against growing US influence on the country."\
  ""\
  "The extremist group, which advocates for cutting diplomatic ties to the US, demands immediate reversal of several recent international cooperation agreements as the condition for release of the hostages."\
  ""\
  "Unwilling to negotiate, the US has invested significant effort into locating the hostages."
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
 }
 U5_Command {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "V. Command/Signals"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Command</h2>"\
  ""\
  "6 - HQ"\
  "1 - Assault Team"\
  "2 - Assault Team"\
  "3 - Support Team"\
  "4 - Reconnaissance Team"\
  "5 - Star flight"\
  ""\
  "Star flight callsigns: Star 51, 52, 53, 54"\
  "Unless planned otherwise, there are initially three MH-6M while one AH-6M provides security. After insertion, two MH-6M pilots switch to the second AH-6M."\
  "Who crews which helicopter is decided by the pilots."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Signals</h2>"\
  ""\
  "Platoon net: 48.0MHz"\
  "Flight net: 48.1MHz"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 U4_Support {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "IV. Service Support"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Service</h2>"\
  "4 MH-6M helicopters are available, only 3 are required for insertion."\
  ""\
  "No resupply/repair/refuel/rearmament available."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Support</h2>"\
  "2 AH-6M with 2 M134 miniguns and 7 Hydra 70 and 2 AGM-114 are available."\
  "It is recommended that one AH-6M provides security during the landing (two-manned if enough pilots are available), and that after insertion, two of the MH-6M pilots man the second one."\
  ""\
  "CAS is coordinated by the FAC."\
  "Fire into the compound is restricted to Type 1 and should ONLY be considered when there is NO possibility of hostages being inadvertently harmed."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 U2_Mission {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "II. Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Mission</h2>"\
  "Secure and extract the hostages, by force or through negotiation."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 U3_Execution {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Commander's Intent</h2>"\
  "The purpose of this operation is to rescue the two hostages."\
  "Elimination of the hostage takers is preferred but not a primary objective."\
  ""\
  "The desired end state is that both hostages and all US forces have been extracted to the starting position."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Concept of Operations</h2>"\
  "The hostages can be secured by force, negotiation or their combination."\
  ""\
  "The reconnaissance team can e. g. be used to secure an LZ, establish a screen ahead of the landing or attempt to gather intelligence on enemy disposition."\
  "While still unsupported by the main force, it should avoid revealing itself or opening fire unless absolutely necessary."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 U6_Negotiation {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "Negotiation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Negotiation</h2>"\
  "Negotiation may become critical to safely securing the hostages."\
  "It should be performed by a designated negotiator (in coordination with the commander), who has been given a radio fully compatible with the enemy radios (their frequency is 52.0MHz)."\
  ""\
  "<b>Example negotiation strategies:</b>"\
  "- Persuade the enemy to let the hostages leave the compound. He is unlikely to accept this as it would make them vurnerable to indiscriminate fire and significantly worsen his tactical situation."\
  "- After the enemy has suffered significant casualties, guarantee surrender in exchange for safety of the hostages."\
  "- Deceive the enemy by pretending to negotiate."\
  "- Propose that remaining enemies can avoid death by leaving, ensured by a couple of remaining guards that could kill the hostages if betrayed."\
  ""\
  "The hostage takers primary motivation is likely their survival. It is unlikely they would kill the hostages unless their capture was imminent and negotiations failed, as they are their main leverage."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
 U1_Situation {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "I. Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Enemy Forces</h2>"\
  "Up to 20 extremists, largely armed with eastern bloc small arms."\
  "Their hideout is an abandoned sawmill compound (Lansikyla Sawmill) in the middle of a forest."\
  "Most enemies are likely within the compound, but it is possibly they may send out patrols."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Friendly Forces</h2>"\
  "The main force is located at 027 036."\
  "The recon team has been forward deployed and is currently standing by within a kilometer of the compound."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 C1_Brief {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "Briefing"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Situation</h2>"\
  "You, US foreign diplomats, have been taken hostage by a group of ~20 armed anti-US extremists and taken to an abandoned sawmill in the middle of a forest."\
  "You cannot flee as there are armed guards watching you."\
  ""\
  "Your captors appear agitated and have retrieved their guns, it looks like they may be expecting some kind of attack."\
  ""\
  "Your goal is to survive."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Rules</h2>"\
  "Make sure to read the hostage rules."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV"
  }
 }
 A7_HostageRules {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "HOSTAGE RULES"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Hostage Rules</h2>"\
  "- While in the presence of hostage takers, the hostage must obey their orders. This can be done reluctantly, but if they would be able to force the hostage to do something, e. g. restrain or move them, they hostage cannot ignore them."\
  "- The hostages must not intentionally risk their life (e. g. do not run away if there is a chance you might get shot), and respond realistically to the threat of violence."\
  "- For the same reason, the hostages cannot simply try to run away on their own, they can only leave the compound when being rescued."\
  "- Hostages must respect reasonable \"roleplay actions\", e. g. they cannot open doors that are closed and presumably locked behind them or move if they were \"restrained\"."\
  "- The hostage takers also have zip cuffs available which can be used to physically restrain the hostage, for that the hostage must surrender by pressing F1."\
  "- The hostage takers cannot bring the hostages away from the compound or swap clothes."\
  "-  While threats can be made, the hostage takers should not kill hostages unless it is deemed absolutely necessary. The hostages are valuable leverage, and there is no inherent benefit to killing them."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV" "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 7
 }
 E1_Situation {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "I. Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Enemy Forces</h2>"\
  "A group associate just reported military helicopters approaching from the south."\
  "This suggests the hideout location has been compromised."\
  "It is too late to move the hostages as some enemies might already be nearby, the only hope is that the attack can be fended off or the hostages can be used as leverage for survival."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Friendly Forces</h2>"\
  "Currently all within the compound (Lansikyla Sawmill), equipped only with small arms."\
  "HQ, 1st team and the first hostage are in the northern two-storey."\
  "2nd team is in the southern warehouse. The second hostage is being held in the southern sawmill building."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 E2_Mission {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "II. Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Mission</h2>"\
  "Ordered by importance, your goals are: Survive, avoid capture, maintain control over the hostages, kill the attackers."\
  ""\
  "You can leave the compound, but the hostages must stay there."\
  ""\
  "Important context can be found in the Execution briefing, also read the hostage rules."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 E3_Execution {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Commander's Intent</h2>"\
  "As described in the mission briefing, the goals are to survive, avoid capture, maintain control over the hostages and if possible, kill the enemy."\
  ""\
  "Killing the hostages is not considered preferable over losing control of them as it does not result in an advantage."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Concept of Operations</h2>"\
  "Not all of these goals may be achievable."\
  "If that is the case, try to achieve a compromise, for example by giving up hostages in exchange for a chance to escape or avoid death."\
  ""\
  "The hostages are very important: They are valuable leverage (allowing for negotiation) and also prevent the enemy from indiscriminately firing at structures as the hostages may come under harm."\
  ""\
  "You may leave the compound, but the hostages must stay inside."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 E4_Support {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "IV. Support"
  m_sTextData "<h2>a. Service</h2>"\
  "The guard teams have zip cuffs nearby which they can use on the hostage if needed."\
  "For them to be used the hostage has to surrender by pressing F1."\
  ""\
  "<h2>b. Support</h2>"\
  "None"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
