  "Platoon net: 52.0MHz"\
  ""\
  "Assume your radio communication might be compromised, use codewords for important messages."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 E6_Negotiation {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "NEGOTIATION"
  m_sTextData "<h2>Negotiation</h2>"\
  "It is possible that you will in one form or another be contacted by the enemy for negotiation purposes."\
  ""\
  "Negotiation may become critical if a continued fight is looking too costly and survival is under serious danger."\
  "Even beyond that, it may be possible to secure some advantages."\
  ""\
  "<b>Some examples:</b>"\
  "- You could offer hostages in exchange for a chance to surrender if the fight is about to be lost."\
  "- Freely giving up the hostages while the fight is still undecided might be unwise as the enemy could decide to attack indiscriminately once the hostages are secure."\
  "- You could attempt delay the enemy by pretending to negotiate."\
  "- You could offer that the enemy can retrieve the hostages after letting "\
  "- Demand that the enemy lets you leave unharmed, with only a couple of guards staying, ready to kill the hostage if the leaving friendlies were attacked."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_SEPARATIST"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
 A8_Notes {
  coords 3472.466 82.781 7140.113
  m_sTitle "Mission Notes"
  m_sTextData "- Setup Timer: 3 minutes, only affects the main US starting position"\
  "Extremists can leave the compound, but not with the hostages."\
  "- Default time is just before dawn, if desired the US commander can request something brighter from GMs during briefing."\
  "- The red rectangle is NOT an AO limit, the extremists can leave the compound."\
  "- Both factions can see an image of the sawmill compound to the right of the AO"\
  ""\
  "End conditions:"\
  "Upon US extraction and rescue/death of both hostages, the mission ends."\
  "Alternatively, the mission can also end at 75% US casualties."\
  "When the game ends, messages about the outcome for all parties are shown."
  m_bShowForAnyFaction 1
  m_iOrder 8
 }
}